=head1 NAME

alg - Get one or more values from BPOM nutrition label reference (ALG, acuan label gizi) (shorter alias for bpom-get-nutrition-label-ref)

=head1 VERSION

This document describes version 0.003 of alg (from Perl distribution App-BPOMUtils-NutritionLabelRef), released on 2024-05-30.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

